Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN 999
Unid=1
!!! *** Length
!!! >>> Length
HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, ZZYZX, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, ZZYZX, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, B, ZZYZX, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, B, ZZYZX, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, ZZYZX, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, B/2, ZZYZX, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, B/2, ZZYZX, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B/2, ZZYZX, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Width
HOTSPOT A, 0, ZZYZX, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, -1, ZZYZX, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, ZZYZX, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -1, ZZYZX, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B, ZZYZX, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Height HOTSPOT 0,B/4,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B/4,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B/4,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,B/4,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B/4,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B/4,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,B*3/4,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B*3/4,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B*3/4,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,B*3/4,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B*3/4,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B*3/4,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1
UnIDTmp = UnID !!! Compatibility requirement - New hotspots UnID = 200
ADDy B/4 h1 = ZZYZX-dtee_h3-dtee_h2 FOR i=0 TO 1 ADDy i*B/2 !!! >>> Web Thickness(Bottom) HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,1+128, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-dtee_thhalf,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,2, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,1,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,3, dtee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,1+128, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,dtee_thhalf,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,2, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,3, dtee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,1+128, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-dtee_thhalf,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,2, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,1,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,3, dtee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,1+128, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,dtee_thhalf,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,2, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,3, dtee_th : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Web Thickness(Top) HOTSPOT A,0,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,1+128, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-dtee_th2half,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,2, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,1,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,3, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,1+128, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,dtee_th2half,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,2, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,3, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,1+128, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-dtee_th2half,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,2, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,1,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,3, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,1+128, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,dtee_th2half,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,2, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1,h1,unID,dtee_th2half,3, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 NEXT i DEL 3
UnID = UnIDTmp !!! Compatibility requirement - New hotspots
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL gs_dtee_mat if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
ADDy B/2 FOR w=1 TO nn*2 PUT GET (2), MAX (-1, 15*GET (1)) NEXT w
ROTz 90 ROTx 90 PRISM_ NSP/3, a, GET (NSP) IF dtee_top_th>0 THEN PRISM_ 4, a, -b/2, zzyzx+0.001, 8, -b/2, zzyzx+dtee_top_th, 13, b/2, zzyzx+dtee_top_th, 8, b/2, zzyzx+0.001, 13 ENDIF DEL 2 DEL 1
999: FOR w=1 TO NSP qq= GET (1) NEXT w
END
Symbol.Script_2D:
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
Unid=1
! --- Length
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, B, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
! --- Width
HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, -1, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -1, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
! --- Length/Axis
HOTSPOT2 0, B/4, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, B/4, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B/4, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, B*3/4, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, B*3/4, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B*3/4, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
! --- Center
HOTSPOT2 A/2, B/2, unID : unID=unID+1
IF only_axis=0 THEN !!! *** Web Thickness IF iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED THEN
UnIDTmp = UnID !!! Compatibility requirement - New hotspots UnID = 200
ADD2 0,B/4 FOR i=0 TO 1 ADD2 0,i*B/2 !!! >>> Web Thickness(Bottom) HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,1+128, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-dtee_thhalf,unID,dtee_thhalf,2, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,1,unID,dtee_thhalf,3, dtee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,1+128, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,dtee_thhalf,unID,dtee_thhalf,2, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-1,unID,dtee_thhalf,3, dtee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,1+128, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-dtee_thhalf,unID,dtee_thhalf,2, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,1,unID,dtee_thhalf,3, dtee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,dtee_thhalf,1+128, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,dtee_thhalf,unID,dtee_thhalf,2, dtee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-1,unID,dtee_thhalf,3, dtee_th : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Web Thickness(Top) HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,dtee_th2half,1+128, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-dtee_th2half,unID,dtee_th2half,2, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,1,unID,dtee_th2half,3, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,dtee_th2half,1+128, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,dtee_th2half,unID,dtee_th2half,2, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-1,unID,dtee_th2half,3, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,dtee_th2half,1+128, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-dtee_th2half,unID,dtee_th2half,2, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,1,unID,dtee_th2half,3, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,dtee_th2half,1+128, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,dtee_th2half,unID,dtee_th2half,2, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-1,unID,dtee_th2half,3, dtee_th2 : unID=unID+1 NEXT i DEL 3
UnID = UnIDTmp !!! Compatibility requirement - New hotspots ENDIF ENDIF
ADD2 0,B/2
FOR I=-1 TO 1 STEP 2 ADD2 0, I*b/4 HOTSPOT2 0, 0 HOTSPOT2 a, 0 DEL 1 NEXT I
!! HOTSPOT2 0, 0, 1, a, 1+256 !! HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, 2, a, 3 !! HOTSPOT2 a, 0, 3, a, 2 !! HOTSPOT2 0, 0
if only_axis=0 then POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, -b/2, 1, 0, b/2, 1, a, b/2, 1, a, -b/2, 1, 0, -b/2, -1
!! HOTSPOT2 0, -b/2 !! HOTSPOT2 0, b/2 !! HOTSPOT2 a, b/2 !! HOTSPOT2 a, -b/2 !! HOTSPOT2 a/2, 0
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then LINE_TYPE DetailLineType for I=-1 TO 1 STEP 2 ADD2 0, I*(b/4) LINE2 0, th1/2, a, th1/2 LINE2 0, -th1/2, a, -th1/2 DEL 1 next I endif endif
if showsect AND only_axis=0 then LINE_TYPE 1 !! HOTSPOT2 0, 0, 21, pos_2Dx, 1+128 !! HOTSPOT2 0, -1', 22, pos_2Dx, 3 !! HOTSPOT2 pos_2Dx, 0, 23, pos_2Dx, 2 ADD2 pos_2Dx, 0 ROT2 90 FILL cross_fill POLY2_ NSP/3, 7, GET (NSP) if dtee_top_th>0 then LINE2 -b/2, zzyzx+dtee_top_th, b/2, zzyzx+dtee_top_th endif DEL 2 endif
if axis then PEN axis_pen LINE_TYPE axis_line_type FOR I=-1 TO 1 STEP 2 ADD2 0, I*b/4 LINE2 0, 0, a, 0 DEL 1 NEXT I endif
DEL 1 END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! iObjectCode PRE_BEAM_DOUBLE_T = 10
rrr = request("Working_length_unit", "", w_units_form) bMetricDimension = strstr(w_units_form, "m") ! m, cm, mm
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
! *** Cross-section Data *** PUT zzyzx, b, dtee_th, dtee_th2, dtee_h2, dtee_h3
IF NSP>=6 THEN zz= GET (1) w1= GET (1) th1= GET (1) th2= GET (1) h2= GET (1) h3= GET (1) zzyzx= zz PARAMETERS zzyzx=zz PARAMETERS b=w1 b= w1 h1= zzyzx-h3-h2 PUT 8 PUT -b/4+th2/2+h2, zz-h3, 1, -b/4+th2/2, h1, 1, -b/4+th1/2, 0, 1, -b/4-th1/2, 0, 1, -b/4-th2/2, h1, 1, -b/4-th2/2-h2, zz-h3, 1, -b/2+0.001, zz-h3, 1, -b/2+0.001, zz, 1 ENDIF
! *** Contour mirroring *** DIM xy[][3]
IF NSP>0 THEN nn = round_int(get(1)) FOR w=1 TO nn xx= GET (1) yy= GET (1) msk= GET (1) PUT xx, yy, msk xy[w][1]= -xx xy[w][2]= yy xy[w][3]= msk NEXT w
FOR w=nn TO 1 STEP -1 PUT xy[w][1], xy[w][2], xy[w][3] NEXT w ENDIF ! *** *** ***

"geometryPage":
x1 = 0 x2 = 140 x3 = 230 x4 = x2 + 100 x5 = x2 + 200 !200 (Style Guide => fillTypeInfLenght) x6 = 400 x7 = 408 xEnd = 444
outfieldHeight = 15 infieldHeight = 19
dy = 24 yEnd = 266 pageStartY = 0 yCurrent = pageStartY + 1
ui_style 0, 0
ui_infield{3} "bTopping", x1, yCurrent, xEnd-x1-2, infieldHeight, 7, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", `Покрытие`, 0, "", `Покрытие`, 1
yCurrent = yCurrent + dy
ui_separator 0, yCurrent, xEnd, yCurrent
uiPictX = 50 uiPictY = yCurrent + 64 uiPictWdt = 243 uiPictHgt = 102 uiPictMargin = 5 uiPictInfWdt = 90
uiPicLeftStart = uiPictX - uiPictInfWdt - uiPictMargin uiPicLeftEND = uiPicLeftStart - uiPictMargin
uiPicTop = uiPictY - uiPictMargin - infieldHeight + 3
uiPicBelow = uiPictY + uiPictHgt + uiPictMargin
uiPicRightStart = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictMargin
if not(bTopping) then UI_PICT 1, uiPictX, uiPictY, uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt, 1 !"PreBeamDT" else UI_PICT 2, uiPictX, uiPictY, uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt, 1 !"PreBeamDT_TOP" endif
ui_infield "dtee_th2", uiPictX+140, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина Стенки Вверху`
if bTopping then ui_infield "dtee_top_th", uiPictX+240, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина Покрытия` endif
ui_infield "dtee_th", uiPictX+138, uiPicBelow, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина Стенки Внизу`
ui_infield "dtee_h3", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+10, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Высота Полки Вверху` ui_infield "dtee_h2", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+30, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Скос Вверху`
return

Symbol.Script_VL:
hideparameter all "A", "B", "Zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "bTopping" then if not(bTopping) then parameters dtee_top_th = 0 lock "dtee_top_th" else parameters dtee_top_th = 0.030 endif endif
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
values{2} "iDet2D" DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, `Простой`
VALUES "a" RANGE (0.3, ) VALUES "b" RANGE [dtee_th2*2+0.1, ) VALUES "dtee_th" RANGE [0.05, b/4] VALUES "dtee_th2" RANGE [0.05, b/4] VALUES "dtee_thhalf" RANGE [0.05/2, b/8] VALUES "dtee_th2half" RANGE [0.05/2, b/8] VALUES "dtee_h2" RANGE [0.02, b/6] VALUES "dtee_h3" RANGE [0.02, ZZYZX-0.1) VALUES "zzyzx" RANGE [MAX (0.15, dtee_h3+dtee_h2+(b/2-dtee_th/2-dtee_h2)/14), )
VALUES "pos_2Dx" RANGE (zzyzx, a)
VALUES "dtee_top_th" RANGE [0,)
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME ="dtee_thhalf" then dtee_th = dtee_thhalf * 2 parameters dtee_th = dtee_th else dtee_thhalf = dtee_th / 2 parameters dtee_thhalf = dtee_thhalf endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME ="dtee_th2half" then dtee_th2 = dtee_th2half * 2 parameters dtee_th2 = dtee_th2 else dtee_th2half = dtee_th2 / 2 parameters dtee_th2half = dtee_th2half endif
if LibraryLangCode = "USA" then VALUES "dtee_sectype" "8TTxx", "8DTxx", "10TTxx", "10DTxx", "12DTxx", "Custom"
if dtee_sectype="8TTxx" then VALUES "dtee_type" "8TT24" endif
if dtee_sectype="8DTxx" then VALUES "dtee_type" "8DT20", "8DT24", "8DT25", "8DT26", "8DT32", "8DT33", "8DT34" endif
if dtee_sectype="10TTxx" then VALUES "dtee_type" "10TT18", "10TT24", "10TT28", "10TT32", "10TT40" endif
if dtee_sectype="10DTxx" then VALUES "dtee_type" "10DT16", "10DT24", "10DT28", "10DT32", "10DT36", "10DT20", "10DT21", "10DT25", "10DT26" endif
if dtee_sectype="12DTxx" then VALUES "dtee_type" "12DT32", "12DT34" endif
